Name: Moreton
Description: The Division of Moreton consists of part of the Brisbane City Council.
ProductsAndIndustry: The area is mainly residential with some light industrial and commercial activities. A light aircraft airport is in Archerfield.
NameDerivation: Named after Morton Bay, the bay bounded by Cape Moreton and Point Lookout. The bay was marked on his chart of May 1770 by Lieutenant James Cook RN, navigator on HM Bark Endeavour.
